reviewText: Pure inspired horror genius!  It's like some people got together & were like "lets cram all the best elements of every campy horror movie into ONE incredible movie!" ...and SEJV was born

This is one of my favorite movies.  Not because of its ability to touch the human spirit, or inspire to greatness, or...well, you get the idea.  It's because it's AWESOME.  Gore, lesbian scenes, too much jungle vampire hotness to handle.  Not to mention a thoroughly amazing plot (and by amazing, I mean a plot that is ridiculously outlandish and yet amazingly is well put together enough to stay interesting).  You will never be bored.  You will never regret this movie.  The fact that you are here looking at this review tells me you are the kind of person that WILL like this movie.

Skin eating jungle vamps tells the tale of a race of Cannibal alien babes from the planet clitorian. A young woman while on trip to the jungles of the amazon is kidnapped by the sexually fueled and bloodthirsty babes and never returns home leaving her family in the states very suspicious of her whereabouts , the woman's sister finally decides after a ton of worrying to come the rescue. Skin eating jungle vamps is full of Great tits, blood and carnage enough to satisfy any gorehound. The sisters finally meet in a crazy climax (literally) you have to see to believe... Featuring The cult superstar- Mr Creepo.
